    {
      "instruction": "<p>When the potatoes have 10 min left, return the reserved pan to a high heat with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once very hot, add the <strong>spiced steak[s]</strong> to the pan</p><p>For rare, cook for 2 min max on each side; for medium-rare, cook for 2-3 min on each side; for medium, cook for 3-4 min on each side</p><p>Transfer the <strong>cooked steak[s]</strong> to a plate to rest for a few min</p>",
