      "instruction": "<p>Slice the <strong>rested steak[s]</strong> finely on a clean board</p><p>Serve the <strong>sliced steak</strong> with the <strong>kachumbari salad</strong> and <strong>viazi karai-style potatoes </strong>to the side</p><p>Dollop the<strong> tamarind chutney</strong> over the steak</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
